sbol:SequenceAnnotation.ns1:description: tetR protein with LVA degradation tag

Tet operator repressor. Binds to the TetO operator (see P12m, P15m) as a tetramer, blocking transcription from the associated promoter. Repression is lifted by binding to tetracycline or its derivative anhydrotetracycline (aTc). Contains no degradation tags (unlike C2d).
